Monalisa Stephen, a Nigerian actor, and social media influencer took to her tweeter handle to caution Singer Teni, whose name is Teniola Apata, not to mock fat people after Teni gave reasons for shredding weight as she said,” I don’t want to die.” In her statement, ” stop putting fat people up for dragging. We live and survive like everyone. Lose weight but stop the BS. fat is not a disease neither is it a problem, but “fat stigma is.” ” be nice. Fat no be disease shut up already and lose your weight in peace.” 